About Reserve


Welcome to Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc.
We are a leading and trusted Appalachian independent oil and gas exploration and production company committed to the safe development of our nation’s abundant energy reserves and the protection of its natural resources.
As a privately-held, family-owned business, Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc’s owners have experienced more than four decades of successful and responsible energy development.  We value strong, positive relationships with our joint venture partners, investors, landowners, service providers and regulators in all aspects of our company’s operations.
Our core values of integrity in all matters, respect for all people touched by our operations, contributing to the success of our business partners, risk-taking, innovation, learning and safety drive our firm commitments to quality, performance and continuous improvement.  Learn more about the Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc. difference, our history and what we do on these pages of our website.

 






