Company Overview of Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc. operates as an independent oil and gas acquisition, development, and production company. The company holds a portfolio of oil and gas producing properties in the Appalachian Basin. It drills and produces wells primarily in Roane, Jackson, Clay, Calhoun, and Kanawha counties located in the west central region of West Virginia. Reserve Oil & Gas, Inc. was founded in 1998 and is based in Spencer, West Virginia.


